# RPI pipeline (v1) — agent index

**Do not treat this file as the full pipeline spec.** Normative step-by-step behavior, gates, filenames, and the **`@rpi-status`** response schema live in the **layered markdown** under [`pipelines/rpi/`](../../pipelines/rpi/). Open the relevant `SPEC.md` for the layer you are executing or reviewing.

## What RPI is here

This workspace runs **[Research–Plan–Implement](https://gist.github.com/y0n1/079f952e5f12857a9ef53a0013f5730e)** plus **`40-verify`**, using **stage specs + scoped `output/<scope>/`** (ICM-style handoffs). Framing, external links, and when to use or skip RPI: **[`pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md)**.

## Layer map (specs)

| Stage | Role (summary) | Spec (full behavior) |
|-------|----------------|----------------------|
| **10-research** | Bootstrap scope; facts-only **`RESEARCH.md`**; optional **`QUESTIONS.md`**; **FAR** gate | [`pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/10-research/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/10-research/SPEC.md) |
| **20-plan** | Executable **`PLAN.md`** with checkboxes; **FACTS** gate | [`pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/20-plan/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/20-plan/SPEC.md) |
| **30-implement** | Mechanical execution from **`PLAN.md`**; **`IMPLEMENTATION_LOG.md`**; pause on failure | [`pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/30-implement/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/30-implement/SPEC.md) |
| **40-verify** | Evidence in **`VERIFICATION.md`**; pass/fail and follow-ups | [`pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/40-verify/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/40-verify/SPEC.md) |

**Pipeline-wide (scopes, artifact chain, triggers):** [`pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md).

## Output layout (reminder)

- **Pattern:** `pipelines/rpi/v1/stages/<stage>/output/<scope>/`
- **`<scope>`** naming, discovery, and artifact sequence (**`SCOPE.md` → `RESEARCH.md` → …**) are defined in **[`pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md)**—do not invent a parallel scheme here.

## Conversation trigger

**`@rpi-status`** — non-destructive status summary. **Normative response shape** (scopes, per-stage files, anomalies, next action): section **Trigger: `@rpi-status`** in **[`pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md`](../../pipelines/rpi/SPEC.md)**.

Human-oriented trigger table: [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) (**Triggers**).

## Submodule implementation

Edits under **`submodules/<name>/`**: branch from that repo’s default branch; superproject gitlink when HEAD changes — **[`.cursor/rules/submodule-git-workflow.mdc`](submodule-git-workflow.mdc)** (also referenced from **30-implement** spec).

## Mission and trackers

Per-project context and inbox format: **`constitutions/<name>/`**; tracker formatting skill: [`constitutions-tracker-format`](../skills/constitutions-tracker-format/SKILL.md).
